snippet.title: Somerford Associates
snippet.description:
We provide innovative Business Intelligence and Information Security solutions to some of the UK's largest companies and Government Departments. 

This channel is an up-to-date library consisting of our dedicated partner Videos, focusing on introductions, demonstrations and case studies, as well as including our past webinar recordings. 

We also offer an array of dedicated complimentary workshops and webinars covering all of our key partner's products, ranging from introductory level classes to more advanced sessions based on your experience with the specified product. Please see our website link below for more information on how you can attend these educational events.
